[1-Hit Kills And Freeze Enemies]
author=bungholio
description=This code is a unusual side effect of the action level modifier. You will want to joker it. Turn it on just before the start or load a game to turn on 1-hit kills. Once 1-hit kills are on you can&#039;t turn it off without quitting to the main menu and setting it to 00. You will want it jokered because you will need to turn it off at times. The 2 pyramid heads at the end of the game can&#039;t be killed if they are frozen. You need to turn it off so they can do their thing where they walk to the center of the room to kill themselves. But otherwise, freeze works fine for most enemies.
patch=1,EE,01224C64,extended,000000FF

