[Better Controllable Camera (Buggy!)]
author=bungholio
description=It doesn&#039;t matter what value you give it, once it&#039;s on you can&#039;t turn it off. It works great with that speed code I made because you can press L2 to change the camera so it follows you very close and doesn&#039;t need to catch up. It doesn&#039;t always work. It can also freeze the game. The game froze in that little motorhome where you get the hyper spray when the camera angle tried to change.
patch=1,EE,01224B86,extended,00000000

