[Room Modifier Thing]
author=bungholio
description=These are digits when you start a new game
02 - you start the exact same way as you normally do
07 - inside the apartment room where you got the flashlight (normal)
13 - inside same hospital room (normal)
1c - inside silent hill historic center building&#039;s save room. Enter prison to make things normal
26 - close by the boat scene outside the level boundaries. turn until you see the light and run towards it to get to the motel, then everything should be normal
28 - inside motel lobby save room (normal)
2c - trapped in room where you fight 2 pyramid heads (they aren&#039;t there, so you are trapped and the doors are locked unless you use the have all items code for the 2 eggs or whatever they were, otherwise it would be normal)
34 - inside the room in the video that mary was in
35 - inside empty hospital, no monsters and you can&#039;t interact with anything


To get to the normal 2 pyramid heads battle, use &quot;28&quot; to start in the hotel lobby, save, shut off code, go to 1st floor of motel and save, turn code back on and load that save to be right outside the door before the battle where you can save.
patch=1,EE,01224BF0,extended,00000002

