[Speed Modifier]
author=bungholio
description=Weird speed modifier, uses float values. The only way to slow down is to move forward or backward with the analog stick. The camera can&#039;t move fast enough to keep up though. Use it with a joker command to control it. Attach it to one button, and as long as you hold that button down you will move very fast. The instant you let go of the button you will return to normal speed.
10 = 41200000 - quite fast
20 = 41a00000 - faster, just fast enough to go through walls
40 = 42200000 - very fast and you can go through walls easily
patch=1,EE,203E70BC,extended,41200000

